				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>Lovely story. I love the way it seems so important to him from the inside (as games do when one is competing)  &#8211; love the vocabulary cross over with live and win; it worked well.</p>
<p>I also like how he loses; unusual ending for a piece like this but it works for me. For me his reaction to losing (realising his mistakes, determined to do better, admitting her superiority) balances his aggression while playing (humiliate her etc) in a cool way.</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

