				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>Nice! I thought something odd was up when Our Hero was attacking his partner, but I did not expect Go 😛 Really great interpretation of &#8220;eye&#8221;.</p>
<p>The piece left me wondering if she&#8217;d been playing him, trying to make him overreact (like with the condescending smile). I like to think that she was, since as the piece says, rash and angered playing doesn&#8217;t win the game. </p>
<p>Some nits:</p>
<p>&gt; lead to death for sure.<br />
I thought that &#8220;for sure&#8221; sounded a bit informal compared to the rest of the piece.</p>
<p>Typo:<br />
&gt; He bowed his head and [thought],</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

